data.value:
This is the third major revision of the "check in" program for the VMware User Group (VMUG). This check in system can be used for other user groups and events beyond VMUG. A special thanks to the VMUG Staff, the leaders of the Cleveland VMUG and other the other known VMUG user groups leveraging the software which I've written.
They include but not limited to: North Central Wisconsin VMUG, Buffalo NY VMUG, Maryland VMUG, New Jersey VMUG
The major reason for this release was to elimate complexities and streamline the process. The pivmugc project was difficult and timely to setup, prone to error additionally alot to maintain. The intent for AttendeeTracker was to have the DYMO printer directly plugged into a laptop, have a single volunteer being in charge of checking in attendees and to natively import/export data from vmug.com.
